<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Pievra - The Agentic Advertising Marketplace</title>
<meta name="description" content="The open marketplace for AI agents in programmatic advertising. 26 agents across AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF and A2A. Find agents, become a partner, follow protocol news."/>
<meta name="keywords" content="AI agent marketplace, agentic advertising, AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF, A2A, programmatic advertising, protocol orchestration"/>
<meta property="og:title" content="Pievra - The Agentic Advertising Marketplace"/>
<meta property="og:description" content="26 AI agents across 5 protocols. The open marketplace for agentic advertising."/>
<meta property="og:url" content="https://pievra.com"/>
<meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/>
<link rel="canonical" href="https://pievra.com"/>

<!-- GA4 Analytics - consent-gated (GDPR/CNIL compliant) -->
<script src="/static/consent.js"></script>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
  --ink: #0a0e1a;
  --ink-soft: #3d4460;
  --ink-muted: #7a829e;
  --surface: #ffffff;
  --surface-2: #f4f5f9;
  --teal: #00c4a7;
  --teal-dark: #009e86;
  --teal-light: #e0faf6;
  --border: #e2e4ed;
  --radius: 12px;
  --radius-lg: 20px;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--surface); color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
h1,h2,h3,h4,h5 { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; line-height: 1.15; }

/* NAV */
nav { background: var(--ink); height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 40px; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
.logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; text-decoration: none; }
.lm { width: 30px; height: 30px; background: var(--teal); border-radius: 7px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink); }
.ln { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 16px; color: #fff; }
.nav-r { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; }
.nav-r a { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; transition: color .2s; }
.nav-r a:hover { color: #fff; }
.nav-r a.active { color: #fff; }
.btn-teal { background: var(--teal); color: var(--ink); font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
.btn-ghost-nav { color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
.btn-ghost-nav:hover { color: #fff; }
.nav-more { position: relative; }
.nav-more-btn { background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2); color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
.nav-more-btn:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); color: #fff; }
.nav-drop { display: none; position: absolute; top: 100%; right: 0; margin-top: 8px; background: var(--ink); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); border-radius: 12px; padding: 8px; min-width: 200px; box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.4); }
.nav-drop.open { display: block; }
.nav-drop a { display: block; padding: 8px 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; border-radius: 8px; transition: all .15s; }
.nav-drop a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); color: #fff; }

/* HERO */
.hero { background: var(--ink); padding: 80px 40px 64px; }
.hero-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
.hero-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: rgba(0,196,167,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(0,196,167,.3); color: var(--teal); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 6px 18px; border-radius: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.hero h1 { font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px); font-weight: 800; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.hero h1 span { color: var(--teal); }
.hero-sub { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.6; }
.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.hero-actions .btn-primary { padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; background: var(--teal); color: var(--ink); }
.hero-actions .btn-outline { padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; background: none; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2); color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); }
.hero-actions a:hover { opacity: .9; transform: translateY(-1px); }
.stats-row { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.stat-cell { text-align: center; }
.stat-num { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 28px; color: var(--teal); }
.stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); margin-top: 2px; }

/* TRUST BAR */
.trust-bar { background: var(--surface-2); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 14px 24px; }
.trust-bar-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.trust-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; }
.trust-items { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.trust-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft); }
.trust-badge { width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; color: white; flex-shrink: 0; }

/* SECTIONS */
.section { padding: 72px 24px; }
.section-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
.section-tag { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal-dark); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.section-title { font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 36px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.section-sub { font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 40px; }

/* THREE PILLARS */
.pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 0; }
.pillar { background: white; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; transition: all .2s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.pillar:hover { border-color: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,196,167,.1); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.pillar-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.pillar-title { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.pillar-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.pillar-meta { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-bottom: 20px; }
.pillar-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: var(--ink); color: white; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; transition: all .15s; }
.pillar-cta:hover { background: #1a2030; }

/* FEATURED AGENTS */
.agents-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
.agent-card { background: white; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; transition: all .15s; }
.agent-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,196,167,.1); }
.agent-card.premium { border-color: var(--teal); background: linear-gradient(135deg, white 0%, var(--teal-light) 100%); }
.agent-head { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.agent-name { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; }
.agent-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.agent-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
.agent-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block; }
.t-adcp { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
.t-mcp { background: #f3e8ff; color: #7e22ce; }
.t-ucp { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
.t-artf { background: #fef9c3; color: #854d0e; }
.t-a2a { background: #ffe4e6; color: #be123c; }
.status-badge { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 20px; }
.status-live { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
.agent-link { background: var(--ink); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 14px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
.agent-link:hover { background: #1a2030; }

/* NEWS PREVIEW */
.news-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
.news-card { background: white; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; transition: all .15s; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block; }
.news-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,196,167,.1); }
.news-badge { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.news-title { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.news-excerpt { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.news-date { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-muted); }

/* CTA BANNER */
.cta-banner { background: var(--ink); padding: 72px 24px; text-align: center; }
.cta-banner h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px); font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.cta-banner p { font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 28px; }

/* FOOTER */
footer { background: var(--ink); padding: 56px 24px 28px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
.footer-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
.footer-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.footer-brand p { font-size: 13px; color: #4a5270; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 12px; max-width: 220px; }
.footer-col h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #8892b0; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
.footer-col ul li a { font-size: 13px; color: #4a5270; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
.footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--teal); }
.footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); padding-top: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: #4a5270; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
.footer-bottom p { font-size: 13px; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  nav { padding: 0 20px; }
  .nav-r a:not(.btn-teal):not(.btn-ghost-nav) { display: none; }
  .nav-more { display: none; }
  .hero { padding: 48px 20px 40px; }
  .pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .agents-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .news-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; }
  .stats-row { gap: 24px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav style="background:#0a0e1a;height:60px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 40px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100">
  <a href="/" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none">
    <div style="width:30px;height:30px;background:#00c4a7;border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Manrope,sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;color:#0a0e1a">P</div>
    <div style="font-family:Manrope,sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:#fff">pievra</div>
  </a>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:center">
    <a href="/marketplace" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Marketplace</a>
    <a href="/partners" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Partners</a>
    <a href="/news" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">News</a>
    <a href="/careers" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Careers</a>
    <a href="/signin" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:500">Sign In</a>
    <a href="/signup" style="background:#00c4a7;color:#0a0e1a;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none">Sign Up Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-pill">26 agents across 5 protocols</div>
    <h1>The agentic advertising <span>marketplace</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Find, compare, and deploy AI agents for programmatic advertising. Every agent across AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF, and A2A in one searchable directory.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/marketplace" class="btn-primary">Browse Agents</a>
      <a href="/partners" class="btn-outline">Find a Partner</a>
      <a href="/news" class="btn-outline">Protocol News</a>
    </div>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">26</div><div class="stat-label">Listed Agents</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">5</div><div class="stat-label">Protocols</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">6</div><div class="stat-label">Categories</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">Free</div><div class="stat-label">Early Access</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRUST BAR -->
<div class="trust-bar">
  <div class="trust-bar-inner">
    <span class="trust-label">Protocol stewards</span>
    <div class="trust-items">
      <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-badge" style="background:#1a56db">AAO</div>Agentic Advertising Org</div>
      <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-badge" style="background:#dc2626">IAB</div>IAB Tech Lab</div>
      <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-badge" style="background:#1e3a5f">LF</div>Linux Foundation</div>
      <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-badge" style="background:#15803d">G</div>Google</div>
      <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-badge" style="background:#4b5563">A</div>Anthropic</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- THREE PILLARS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="pillars">
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">🤖</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Agent Marketplace</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">The open directory of every AI agent, MCP server, and protocol tool in agentic advertising. Sourced from AdCP, IAB AAMP, Prebid, A2A, and the IAB Agent Registry.</p>
        <p class="pillar-meta">26 agents &middot; 6 categories &middot; 5 protocols</p>
        <a href="/marketplace" class="pillar-cta">Browse All Agents &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Partner Directory</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Find implementation experts, technology vendors, and consultancies who can help you deploy AI agents for programmatic advertising.</p>
        <p class="pillar-meta">Open for applications &middot; 7 categories</p>
        <a href="/partners" class="pillar-cta">Find a Partner &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">📰</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Protocol News</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">In-depth analysis of every AI protocol shaping programmatic advertising. Real launch dates, correct versions, verified facts.</p>
        <p class="pillar-meta">5 protocol deep-dives &middot; Weekly updates</p>
        <a href="/news" class="pillar-cta">Read Latest &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURED AGENTS -->
<section class="section" style="background:var(--surface-2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">Featured Open Source Projects</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Agents you can deploy today</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Real open source projects from Prebid, IAB Tech Lab, and the AdCP ecosystem. Every listing links to its source repo.</p>

    <div class="agents-grid">
      <div class="agent-card premium">
        <div class="agent-head">
          <div>
            <div class="agent-name">Prebid Sales Agent</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:3px">Media Trading &middot; Prebid.org</div>
          </div>
          <span class="status-badge status-live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-desc">Open-source publisher-side AI agent that automates programmatic ad sales. Exposes inventory via MCP, integrates with Google Ad Manager. Deploy via Docker in 2 minutes.</div>
        <div class="agent-meta">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:6px">
            <span class="agent-tag t-adcp">AdCP</span><span class="agent-tag t-mcp">MCP</span><span class="agent-tag t-a2a">A2A</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/prebid/salesagent" target="_blank" class="agent-link">View on GitHub &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="agent-card premium">
        <div class="agent-head">
          <div>
            <div class="agent-name">IAB Buyer Agent</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:3px">Media Trading &middot; IAB Tech Lab</div>
          </div>
          <span class="status-badge status-live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-desc">AI-powered media buying system built on CrewAI and IAB OpenDirect 2.1. Receives campaign briefs, allocates budget across channels, and books deals programmatically.</div>
        <div class="agent-meta">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:6px">
            <span class="agent-tag t-mcp">MCP</span><span class="agent-tag t-a2a">A2A</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/IABTechLab/buyer-agent" target="_blank" class="agent-link">View on GitHub &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="agent-card premium">
        <div class="agent-head">
          <div>
            <div class="agent-name">AdCP Protocol Server</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:3px">Infrastructure &middot; AgenticAdvertising.org</div>
          </div>
          <span class="status-badge status-live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-desc">Official reference implementation of the Ad Context Protocol. Campaign negotiation, deal management, and media buy protocols with Express server and OpenAPI specs.</div>
        <div class="agent-meta">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:6px">
            <span class="agent-tag t-adcp">AdCP</span><span class="agent-tag t-mcp">MCP</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/adcontextprotocol/adcp" target="_blank" class="agent-link">View on GitHub &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:32px">
      <a href="/marketplace" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--ink);color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none">Browse all 26 agents &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LATEST NEWS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">Protocol Intelligence</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Latest protocol analysis</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">In-depth coverage of every agentic advertising protocol. Verified facts, real launch dates, no hype.</p>

    <div class="news-grid">
      <a href="/news" class="news-card">
        <div class="news-badge t-adcp">AdCP</div>
        <h3 class="news-title">Ad Context Protocol (AdCP) - The Open Standard That Launched Agentic Advertising</h3>
        <p class="news-excerpt">First open standard enabling AI agents to execute advertising tasks across any platform. 20+ founding members, built on MCP and A2A.</p>
        <div class="news-date">October 15, 2025 &middot; 9 min read</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/news" class="news-card">
        <div class="news-badge t-mcp">MCP</div>
        <h3 class="news-title">Model Context Protocol - From Anthropic Side Project to Linux Foundation Standard</h3>
        <p class="news-excerpt">Universal context exchange and tool-connection standard with 97M+ monthly downloads. Now under Linux Foundation governance.</p>
        <div class="news-date">November 25, 2025 &middot; 8 min read</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/news" class="news-card">
        <div class="news-badge t-artf">ARTF</div>
        <h3 class="news-title">ARTF v1.0 - IAB Tech Lab's Framework That Promises to Cut RTB Latency by 80%</h3>
        <p class="news-excerpt">Containerisation architecture targeting RTB round-trip from 600-800ms to ~100ms. Public comment period opened January 2026.</p>
        <div class="news-date">November 13, 2025 &middot; 7 min read</div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:32px">
      <a href="/news" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--ink);color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none">Read all protocol news &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BANNER -->
<div class="cta-banner">
  <div style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px">🐙</div>
  <h2>Five protocols. One marketplace.</h2>
  <p>Pievra aggregates every AI agent across all five agentic advertising protocols into one searchable directory.</p>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
